<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1020] Regionserver OOME handler should dump vital stats</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1020</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On OOME the regionserver should dump into the log some vital stats:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Number of regions&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Number of store files&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Estimated item count and size of memcache(s)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Estimated item count and size of store file indexes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Assumes the reserve can be released upon OOME to allow the additional actions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
