                                                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="12649984" author="stack" created="Sat, 22 Nov 2008 23:23:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can just dump current metrics to log; has region count, and store file count.  Memcache metric has size, not item count (Might be possible to add this as metric &amp;#8211; I think we keep it.. not so for store files).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12649989" author="apurtell" created="Sun, 23 Nov 2008 00:52:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll add metrics for store file indexes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12650479" author="stack" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2008 06:53:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to dump metrics on OOME/abort.  Patch also does &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1006&quot; title=&quot;Resevoir of memory not freed on OOME&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1006&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1006&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; adding in checks for OOME all over HRS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;May still be some holes where an OOME will escape and not be caught and abort-handled.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12650480" author="stack" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2008 06:54:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Making patch available.  Review appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12650695" author="apurtell" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2008 19:20:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. With &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1022&quot; title=&quot;Add  storefile index size to hbase metrics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1022&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1022&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; in also this is good. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If OOME escapes I assume there will be a stack trace and we can reopen this issue to fix based on reports of them, correct?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12650758" author="stack" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2008 21:50:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the review Andrew.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
